{"an3.45:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 3.45 ","an3.45:0.2":"5. Culavagga ","an3.45:0.3":"Panditasutta ","an3.45:1.1":"“Tinimani, bhikkhave, panditapannattani sappurisapannattani. ","an3.45:1.2":"Katamani tini? ","an3.45:1.3":"Danam, bhikkhave, panditapannattam sappurisapannattam. ","an3.45:1.4":"Pabbajja, bhikkhave, panditapannatta sappurisapannatta. ","an3.45:1.5":"Matapitunam, bhikkhave, upatthanam panditapannattam sappurisapannattam. ","an3.45:1.6":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, tini panditapannattani sappurisapannattaniti. ","an3.45:2.1":"Sabbhi danam upannattam, ","an3.45:2.2":"ahimsa samyamo damo; ","an3.45:2.3":"Matapitu upatthanam, ","an3.45:2.4":"santanam brahmacarinam. ","an3.45:3.1":"Satam etani thanani, ","an3.45:3.2":"yani sevetha pandito; ","an3.45:3.3":"Ariyo dassanasampanno, ","an3.45:3.4":"sa lokam bhajate sivan”ti. ","an3.45:3.5":"Pancamam. "}